                                <div class="sec-title">
                                    <div class="title">About Us</div>
                                    <h2>Pahadi Rasyan</h2>
                                </div>
                                <div class="text">Pahadi Rasyan, founded by Pushpa Bisht, brings the pure, organic
                                    produce of Uttarakhand to urban cities like Mumbai. We offer 100% chemical-free,
                                    farm-fresh products, including Pahadi Rajma, organic mandua flour, and Himalayan
