                            <div class="inner-column">
                                <div class="sec-title">
                                    <div class="title">Our founder's vision</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="text">Pahadi Rasyan, founded by Pushpa Bisht, is dedicated to sustainable
                                    agriculture and supporting Uttarakhand’s farmers. Inspired by the challenges local
                                    farmers face, Pushpa aims to connect their fresh, chemical-free produce to urban
